RCBC is a simple COLLADA model parser and renderer library written in C for a uni project.
This is far from production ready and has been abandonded. See ColladaCPP for a slightly better C++ version.

To build:
=========
'make'

To Install:
===========
'make install'

Libraries:
=========
libmxml-dev
glut (freeglut3-dev)
libdevil-dev
